    <mxCell id="note" value="&lt;b&gt;Heat input&lt;/b&gt; is set by regulating saturated-steam pressure, hence jacket temperature T&lt;sub&gt;s&lt;/sub&gt;.&#10;&lt;b&gt;Heat removal&lt;/b&gt; is set by the coolant flow rate F&lt;sub&gt;c&lt;/sub&gt;, which fixes the coil coefficient U&lt;sub&gt;c&lt;/sub&gt;:&#160; 1/U&lt;sub&gt;c&lt;/sub&gt; = 1/(4550 F&lt;sub&gt;c&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;sup&gt;0.8&lt;/sup&gt;) + 1/10.8&#10;&#961;C&lt;sub&gt;p&lt;/sub&gt;V dT/dt = k&lt;sub&gt;1&lt;/sub&gt;C&lt;sub&gt;A&lt;/sub&gt;&#178;(&#8722;&#916;H&lt;sub&gt;1&lt;/sub&gt;)V + k&lt;sub&gt;2&lt;/sub&gt;C&lt;sub&gt;B&lt;/sub&gt;(&#8722;&#916;H&lt;sub&gt;2&lt;/sub&gt;)V + U&lt;sub&gt;j&lt;/sub&gt;A&lt;sub&gt;j&lt;/sub&gt;(T&lt;sub&gt;s&lt;/sub&gt; &#8722; T) &#8722; U&lt;sub&gt;c&lt;/sub&gt;A&lt;sub&gt;c&lt;/sub&gt;(T &#8722; T&lt;sub&gt;c&lt;/sub&gt;)" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#cccccc;fillColor=#f7f7f7;spacing=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="100" y="620" width="800" height="76" as="geometry"/>
    </mxCell>

    <mxCell id="caveat" value="A&lt;sub&gt;j&lt;/sub&gt;/V = 30 m&#8315;&#185;, A&lt;sub&gt;c&lt;/sub&gt;/V = 17 m&#8315;&#185;. Reactor volume, vessel dimensions and coil geometry are not specified in the paper.&#10;The paper gives no process schematic; this diagram is composed from its text. Grey dashed nozzles (charge, discharge) and the agitator are inferred, not stated." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;fontColor=#777777;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacing=4;" vertex="1" parent="1">
